## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="ef61a-102">只有裝載於 IIS 或 WAS 的服務才會顯示這個擴充部分。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef61a-102">This extension is present only for services hosted in IIS or WAS.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef61a-103">服務可以從自身的 <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase> 擷取這個擴充部分，以判斷其是否裝載於 IIS 或 WAS，如下列範例所示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef61a-103">Services can determine whether they are hosted in IIS or WAS by retrieving this extension from their <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>, as shown in the following example.</span></span>  



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="ef61a-104">下列範例顯示如何從服務主機復原 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activation.VirtualPathExtension>，並傳回值，表示其裝載於 IIS 或是 WAS。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef61a-104">The following example shows how to recover the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activation.VirtualPathExtension> from the service host and return a value that it is hosted in IIS or WAS.</span></span>  

```csharp  
bool isHosted = false;  
ServiceHostBase host = OperationContext.Current.Host;  
VirtualPathExtension vpe = host.Extentions.Find<VirtualPathExtension>();  

if( vpe != null )  
Console.WriteLine("The virtualPath of the hosted Service is  {0}", vpe.VirtualPath);  
```
